snippet.title: Lee Cole III
snippet.description: Welcome to Lee Cole 111 channel. This station will be mostly a true crime station with true facts and also backed up facts. We will have interviews with the very people that lived the life. We are looking to set an example for those who have turned their lives around despite the many struggles that they are having or have had. We will also call out the fakes that give a bad name to those who have legitimately turned their lives around. Our videos will be done live and not be video's that are edited . I believe that a live video brings out the reality in the video and in the people in the video. Debate and different opinions are expected as long as they are respective and not attacking the people in the video's. We are hoping to become a great entertainment value for those looking for facts and every once in a while some opinions. If you like the show please like and subscribe. We will try to get better with each and every show, this way we bring you a great and entertaining show.
